About
Engine No9 is a prime burger sports bar in the heart of St. Petersburg's Edge District. We opened in September 2012 and have been a culinary destination ever since. We won best burger from 2013-19 and are considered one of the best burgers in the state.
Nestled on the corner of 1st Ave N and 9th St., Engine No9  is a small sports bar with a strong hockey vibe.
Owner Jason Esposito was born into a family of hockey royalty. His father, Tony Esposito, and his uncle, Phil Esposito, are both in the hockey hall of fame, as well as the founders of the Tampa Bay Lightning team.
